<topic id="testedplatformsandtools" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title>Tested platforms and tools</title>
  <titlealts>
    <navtitle>Tested Platforms and tools</navtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <shortdesc>See which tools and platforms have been used in testing the DITA 
    processing system.</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <p>The DITA processing system has been tested against the following 
      platforms and tools:</p>
    <simpletable>
      <strow>
        <stentry>Tested OS:</stentry>
        <stentry>Windows XP, SLES 10</stentry>
      </strow>
      <strow>
        <stentry>Tested XSLT processor:</stentry>
        <stentry>Xalan-J 2.6, Saxon 6.5<note>XSLT 2.0 standard is not supported yet, 
          don't use XSLT 2.0 engines. For example: Saxon 8.x.</note></stentry>
      </strow>
      <strow>
        <stentry>Tested JDK:</stentry>
        <stentry>IBM 1.5, SUN 1.5</stentry>
      </strow>
      <strow>
        <stentry>Tested Ant:</stentry>
        <stentry>Ant 1.7.1</stentry>
      </strow>
    </simpletable>
  </body>
</topic>